All Implemented Interfaces:
ResultTrait, LanguageTrait, SilentTryTrait, TryTrait, Broadcaster, Listener, Repeater, RepeaterMixin, Transceiver, ProjectTrait, RegistryTrait, JavaTrait, TripwireTrait, Receiver, Transmitter, NamedObject, Mixin, PackageTrait, org.junit.rules.TestRule
public class KryoUnitTest extends UnitTest
Adds Kryo serialization testing to the UnitTest base class. Serialization of objects can be tested with:
  • testSerialization(Object)
  • testSerialization(Object, Version)
  • testSessionSerialization(Object)

The registered types used by these methods can be specified by overriding kryoTypes().
